data.description: Welcome to resort living in Lake Camelot! This beautiful & updated 4-bedroom, 3 full-bathroom, 1-half-bath home features stunning archways, a cozy fireplace, tons of natural light and Brazilian cherry hardwood flooring. The updated kitchen includes granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, tons of storage and more! The primary suite offers a cathedral ceiling and a full private bath. The basement includes a fourth bedroom and extra living space/rec room with new flooring. Totally move-in ready and waiting for you to call it home!
